💯 KICK ASS COLLEGIATE CONFIDENCE 📓 

.

Bang Energy is getting your fall semester prep done early this year with the Bangin’ Back to School Energy Sweepstakes!glowing star 3 lucky winners could win:

💻 MacBook Pro 13.3”

🎧 Apple Air Pods Pro

⌚️Apple iWatch

.

For your chance to win follow the 3 simple steps below:

1️⃣ GO to @BangEnergySweepstakes & share their post to your story. *𝘔𝘢𝘬𝘦 𝘴𝘶𝘳𝘦 𝘺𝘰𝘶𝘳 𝘢𝘤𝘤𝘰𝘶𝘯𝘵 𝘪𝘴 𝘰𝘯 𝘱𝘶𝘣𝘭𝘪𝘤.*

3️⃣ SIGN-UP at www.Bangenergy.com/sweepstakes to complete your entry. .

This sweepstakes begins at 09:00:00AM Eastern Time (“EST”) on Monday, 7/19/2021 and closes at 11:59PM EST on Friday 7/23/2021. Three winners will be chosen from eligible entrants, at random, and announced Thursday 7/29/2021! 🏆 

.

No purchase necessary. Exclusions apply. Terms & conditions here: www.Bangenergy.com/sweepstakes

.

Follow the inventor of Bang: @bangenergy.ceo 😎

OFF THE RAILS 7-ELEVEN EXCLUSIVE FLAVOR! 🛹

.

🚨We are BRINGING THE BANG with the new Bang Energy Swirly Pop Flavor Launch exclusively at 7-Eleven! On July 11th, make sure to celebrate this epic event by picking up the all #NEW Swirly Pop Bang Energy and getting a #FREE Slurpee! 

.

Bang Energy is celebrating with a #giveaway of some exclusive Swirly Pop collab-themed gear! Check out how you can enter to win an exclusive hat, T-shirt, skateboard, deck stickers, and a free case of the NEW Swirly Pop!

1️⃣ FEED POST a photo of you with your purchased Swirly Pop from 7-Eleven.

2️⃣TAG @BangEnergy,@BangEnergy.CEO 
& #SwirlyPop

3️⃣ SIGN-UP at BangEnergyGiveaway.com (entrants who skip this step won't be eligible).

.

5 Winners will be chosen and announced on the Bang Energy IG Story Friday 7/16.

.

Follow the inventor of Bang: @bangenergy.ceo 😎 

.
